754
00:39:52,320 --> 00:39:52,920
Really?

755
00:39:53,599 --> 00:39:54,280
Really.

756
00:39:55,119 --> 00:39:55,800
It's the truth.

757
00:40:01,719 --> 00:40:02,800
Get me a room.

758
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:05,199
I'm sorry.

759
00:40:05,320 --> 00:40:07,199
We're full up.

760
00:40:09,440 --> 00:40:10,159
Full?

761
00:40:10,440 --> 00:40:11,320
Yes.

762
00:40:11,519 --> 00:40:12,480
When you come again,

763
00:40:12,480 --> 00:40:14,480
I'll prepare a good room for you.

764
00:40:16,119 --> 00:40:16,880
Sir.

765
00:40:20,360 --> 00:40:22,320
Please let this officer use my room.

766
00:40:31,040 --> 00:40:32,544
(Yong'an Pawnshop)

767
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:42,119
Here it is.

768
00:40:55,440 --> 00:40:57,679
So this is the map
of the Altar Treasure?

